 directed the preclinical and clinical development of several enzymes for cardiovascular disease and metabolic disorders was awarded several patents for work related to these enzymes and authored related papers he held several senior positions with biomarin pharmaceutical inc continental pharma cryosan inc and ibex technologies which he founded he serves as chairman of the board of eloxx pharmaceuticals ltd he has been an independent director of ra pharmaceuticals inc since march  he has been a director at clementia pharmaceuticals inc since june  he serves as a director of lumos pharma inc zingenix ltd and visiongate inc he served as a director of the canadian genetic diseases network and alexion montréal corp he served as a director of biocapital he served as a director of ibex technologies inc from may   to december   he also serves on the advisory board of sectoral asset management he served as a director of the industrial biotechnology association of canada he was awarded several patents in the field of coagulation phenylketonuria and hypophosphatasia and has published in these fields he has also received several awards for his work including company of the year gold leaf award for enobia pharma   biotecanada entrepreneur of the year  canada  canadian venture capital association genesis award   from bioquebec dr heft received a bachelor of mechanical engineering from mcgill university and a masters degree in nuclear engineering from cornell university before obtaining his phd from the massachusetts institute of technology in genetic engineeringradiological sciences in  and was a neurology fellow at the massachusetts general hospitalread full background corporate headquarters  rachel street eastmontreal quebec hw acanadaphone fax  board members memberships chief executive officer and directoralexion montréal corpdirectorvisiongate incdirectorlumos pharma incpresentdirectorclementia pharmaceuticals incpresentindependent directorra pharmaceuticals inc education ma